Text: "My travel story in Peru during the road to Cuzco since Tulcan in Equator in\
  \ the bus of Panamerican Enterprise in 18 hours until Huaquillas, and   then Huaquillas-\
  \ Aguas Verdes (Per\xFA Frontier), Tumbes-Lima ( 12 hours); Lima-Cuzco 30 hours\
  \ by the road around the Pacifical Coast. In Cuzco arrive to the Hostal where i\
  \ need a good bath , but don't warm water. I use the cold water . After the bath\
  \ the reaction of the Body and organism; and then I need several \"Mates de Coca\
  \ \" to estabilizing my arterial pression. \n\nIn  two weeks get adaptation, and\
  \ then was more easy my quotidiane existence."
